
'''''The First Grader''''' ni filime yikinamico ya biografiya ya 2010 iyobowe na Justin Chadwick . Irimo Naomie Harris, Oliver Litondo, na Tony Kgoroge . Iyi filime ishingiye ku nkuru y'impamo ya Kimani Maruge, [[Kenya|umuhinzi wo muri Kenya]] wiyandikishije mu mashuri abanza afite imyaka 84 nyuma yaho guverinoma ya Kenya yatangaje ko amashuri abanza ari buntu ku isi mu 2003. 

