=== Gufata amashusho ===
[[Dosiye:Africa6_006.jpg|right|thumb| Ikibaya kinini cya Rift muri Kenya, ahabereye amashusho.]]
Producer ukomoka muri Amerika witwa Sam Feuer yasanze inkuru kurupapuro rwambere rwa LA Times ahitamo  We, hanyuma, ashaka umufatanyabikorwa Richard Harding, yafatanije na BBC Films maze aha akazi Ann Peacock kwandika amashusho. Filime yakozwe n’abongereza yafatiwe  ahitwa Rift Valley muri Kenya, nubwo mbere byavuzwe ko izafatirwa muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika yepfo]] . Umuyobozi Chadwick yagize ati: "Twashoboraga kuyirasa muri Afurika y'Epfo, ariko Kenya ifite izo mbaraga zidasanzwe, zidasobanutse zirangwa mu bana, ndetse n'abantu twakoraga film". <ref>Interview with director Justin Chadwick, reproduced by Soda Pictures. Theatrical Press Kit. Retrieved 2015-12-15.</ref>

